{"tid":100081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]周庭、香港中箭成員年宵有份賣老翻","createTime":"2017-01-29T16:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T06:41:41.000Z","uid":7775,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ec02f938effbd9c3b6178976aa39f9207009cc","tid":100081,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hugegod/posts/753560244795726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhugegod%2Fposts%2F753560244795726&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fc705467\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hugegod/posts/753560244795726</a><br />\n<br />\n維園年宵曲終人散<br />\n部分攤位剽竊他人設計製作物品圖利，畀一眾巴絲圍插<br />\n<br />\n其中包括<span style=\"color: red;\">維園164檔</span>賣中咗輻射既Pokemon<br />\n<br />\n令小弟驚訝既係，竟然<span style=\"color: red;\">周庭同其他與中箭關係密切既人</span>都有份搞依檔野！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0q54OU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0q54OU.jpg&h=be803237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4Tj4wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4Tj4wk.jpg&h=09ef7135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n檔位攪手之一同周庭、中箭關係密切，無花無假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/004903_adc02a4397bdbf0c638730fa641c2a70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F004903_adc02a4397bdbf0c638730fa641c2a70.jpg&h=07bd895a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwbB6So.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwbB6So.jpg&h=dd06d10f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ff611c5b2d1968b3c290a5ce13d59b39fe5ca10","tid":100081,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"多謝中箭，檔主Ivan Wong 賣哂存貨<br />\n<br />\n今次肥仔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i